comment.body:
@baentsch thanks for the pointer to the ci repo in the PR.

I think the observation here is that we could/should update the CI image, so could we transfer this issue over to https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/ci-containers

In terms of https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/tsc/issues/5 I think ensuring efficiency is important, but we should review the base & additional dependencies 'periodically' (tools like dependabot can help, and be scheduled to run, for example, monthly - and sites like quay.io can help with (free) image scans)
